  <div class="container flex">
    <div class="description-feature-1" >
      <h1 style="text-align:center;">READ GREAT STORIES</h1>
      <h1 style="text-align:center;">BEFORE ANYONE ELSE</h1>
      <p style="text-align:center;">Read Chapter Exclusives from your favourite web fiction authors.</p>
      <p style="text-align:center;">Unlock the chapters that only Chapter members can see.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="example-classname" data-section-name="feature-2" style="height: 676px; background-color: rgb(75, 164, 207);">
  <div class="container flex">
    <div class="description-feature-2" >
      <h1 style="text-align:center;">SERIOUSLY SERIAL</h1>
      <p style="text-align:center;">Purchase stories by the chapter, and follow the story as it unfolds.</p>
      <p style="text-align:center;">Never buy a book again and realise it’s not for you.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="example-classname" data-section-name="feature-3" style="height: 676px; background-color: rgb(253, 124, 39);">
  <div class="container flex">
    <div class="description-feature-3" >
      <h1 style="text-align:center;">SUPPORT</h1>
      <h1 style="text-align:center;">BRILLIANT AUTHORS</h1>
      <p style="text-align:center;">We believe talented authors should be able to write whenever they want,</p>
      <p style="text-align:center;">not when they can fit it in around their day job.</p>
      <p style="text-align:center;">With Chapter, authors can earn a living from writing—</p>
      <p style="text-align:center;">so you’ll never be left waiting for weekly updates again.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
